pageContext.claim: “The last thing we need in Alabama and the U.S. Senate is a Schumer/Pelosi puppet who is WEAK on Crime, WEAK on the Border, Bad for our Military and our great Vets, Bad for our 2nd Amendment, AND WANTS TO RAISES TAXES TO THE SKY. Jones would be a disaster!”
pageContext.analysis: Trump tweeted a video originally shared by the far-right activist group Britain First, which claimed to show a Muslim migrant. But the Dutch prosecutor said the man shown was arrested and was not a Muslim; he was born and raised in the Netherlands. The Dutch embassy even tweeted to Trump: “The perpetrator of the violent act in this video was born and raised in the Netherlands." Trump has never acknowledged the error.
